properties.description: GrillPro Electric Table Top Grill
properties.full_description: The GrillPro Electric Table Top Grill offers up the performance you would expect from a portable gas grill in a convenient, compact electric grill. The powerful 1,500-Watt/120-Volt electric cooking element heats up quickly to get you grilling fast and offers up a wide range of control to let you get to your desired cooking temperature. The cast iron cooking grid retains the heat to provide a great sear, adding another layer of flavor to your food. The folding legs allow the grill to be easily stored when not in use. This grill is intended for outdoor use only and is ideal for grillers in apartments, condos, or any other residence where use of gas or charcoal grills is restricted.
